@startuml UserAuthentication State Machine
title User Authentication - State Machine Diagram
left to right direction

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor#E8F5E9
    BorderColor#388E3C
    ArrowColor#424242
}

[*] --> UNREGISTERED : New user

UNREGISTERED --> REGISTERED : Submit registration\n(email required)

REGISTERED --> UNVERIFIED : Account created\n(email sent)

UNVERIFIED --> VERIFIED : Email link clicked\n(verification token)
UNVERIFIED --> REGISTERED : Registration expired\n(resubmit)
UNVERIFIED --> LOCKED : Too many failed attempts

VERIFIED --> ACTIVE : First login successful\nor Admin approval

ACTIVE --> SUSPENDED : Admin action\n(policy violation)
ACTIVE --> LOCKED : Too many failed logins
ACTIVE --> ACTIVE : Normal login/logout
ACTIVE --> PASSWORD_RESET : Password reset requested

PASSWORD_RESET --> ACTIVE : Password changed\nvia reset link

SUSPENDED --> ACTIVE : Admin unsuspends
SUSPENDED --> LOCKED : Admin locks account

LOCKED --> ACTIVE : Admin unlocks

LOCKED --> [*] : Account deleted\n(permanent deletion)
ACTIVE --> [*] : Account deleted\n(by user or admin)

' ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' NOTES
' ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

note right of UNVERIFIED
  Verification token valid for 24h
  Resend option available
  Login restricted until verified
end note

note right of LOCKED
  Requires admin intervention
  All sessions terminated
  Password reset required on unlock
end note

note right of PASSWORD_RESET
  Reset link sent to email
  Single-use token (1 hour validity)
  Old password invalidated
end note

@enduml
